{"word":"G4759 - στρατοπεδάρχης - stratopedárchēs - strat-op-ed-ar'-khace - Captain of the guard","slug":"G4759","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στρατοπεδάρχης</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>stratopedárchēs"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>strat-op-ed-ar'-khace"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Captain of the guard"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x03B4;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C7;&#x03B7;&#x03C2; - stratopedarche&#x0304;s</b> - <i>strat-op-ed-ar'-khace</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4760\">G4760</a> and <a href=\"#/G757\">G757</a>; a <i>ruler of an army</i>, that is, (specifically) a Praetorian <i>praefect:</i> - captain of the guard."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4752\">G4752</a>, <a href=\"#/G4753\">G4753</a>, <a href=\"#/G4754\">G4754</a>, <a href=\"#/G4755\">G4755</a>, <a href=\"#/G4756\">G4756</a>, <a href=\"#/G4757\">G4757</a>, <a href=\"#/G4758\">G4758</a>, <a href=\"#/G4760\">G4760</a>"}]}